sub_title: Data Analyst | Technologies and Politics Researcher
summary:
Data Analyst with a background in IT and social sciences research. Advanced command of SQL, Python and MS Excel coupled with excellent writing skills and proficiency in English, Russian and Kazakh. 

My areas of expertise are sustainability, technologies and politics, mixed research methods, as well as written and visual communications.
